    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_4_10594-10633",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "10594-10633",
      "markText": "中国历史上的皇朝常常是这样，只要这个皇帝还健在，他要折腾，你就一点办法也没有。",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10594&rangeEnd=10633",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10594&rangeEnd=10633"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_4_8258-8312",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8258-8312",
      "markText": "事实上，崇祯皇帝对于继续生存下去已经完全丧失信心——他对自己丧失信心，对群臣丧失信心，对大明也已经丧失信心。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8258&rangeEnd=8312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8258&rangeEnd=8312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_5_12377-12404",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "12377-12404",
      "markText": "所以说，明朝的亡国和文官的主流群体放弃明朝有直接关系。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12377&rangeEnd=12404",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12377&rangeEnd=12404"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_6_1276-1356",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1276-1356",
      "markText": "中国人很多时候都把男人干坏事归罪于女人，比如，把商纣王亡国归罪于妲己，把周幽王亡国归罪于褒姒。他们也不想想，就算没有郑贵妃，万历皇帝难道不会有王贵妃、冯贵妃吗？",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1276&rangeEnd=1356",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1276&rangeEnd=1356"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_5_9949-10046",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9949-10046",
      "markText": "明朝就形成了这种很有意思的风气：士大夫向皇帝提意见，皇帝要对他进行惩罚——或者是责骂，或者是廷杖，或者是罢官。但是士大夫受廷杖或者被罢官以后，出了皇宫，出了北京，声誉就更高了，大家都更加钦佩他。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9949&rangeEnd=10046",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9949&rangeEnd=10046"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_4_3163-3241",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3163-3241",
      "markText": "面临如此严重的内忧外患，崇祯皇帝能怎么办？他难免会举措失当。这其实是个恶性循环，形势越恶化，人心中越着急；人心中越着急，举措越失当；举措越失当，形势越恶化。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3163&rangeEnd=3241",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3163&rangeEnd=3241"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_9_6578-6643",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6578-6643",
      "markText": "但是，我仍然不改变对崇祯皇帝的同情，即便他慌不择路，病急乱投医，但坦率地说，那个时候换成你我做皇帝，也未必能比崇祯皇帝表现得更好。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6578&rangeEnd=6643",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6578&rangeEnd=6643"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_5_9078-9118",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9078-9118",
      "markText": "晚明的一个极大的问题是，几乎所有人都在意气用事，没有方寸，没有规矩，更没有是非。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9078&rangeEnd=9118",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9078&rangeEnd=9118"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_6_1959-1999",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1959-1999",
      "markText": "我有时候也不理解，李太后本来是很有主见的，为什么在这个问题上没有和儿子站在一起？",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1959&rangeEnd=1999",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1959&rangeEnd=1999"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_6_9156-9195",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9156-9195",
      "markText": "无论是东林党还是阉党，都认为自己是正确的，都认为自己是正人，都斥责对方是奸邪。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9156&rangeEnd=9195",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9156&rangeEnd=9195"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_4_2193-2256",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2193-2256",
      "markText": "我有时在想，如果身为父亲的明神宗朱翊钧多活两个月，或者朱常洛少活两个月，明朝不就没有这个光宗了吗？命运真是折腾人，也折腾明朝。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2193&rangeEnd=2256",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2193&rangeEnd=2256"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_6_7951-8040",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7951-8040",
      "markText": "我想强调一个事实：几乎所有时代文官和宦官的斗争，都是以文官失败而告终的。为什么？因为疏不间亲。文官们根本不知道皇帝在想什么。他们认为的天大的事情，在皇帝那里，其实根本就不是事情。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7951&rangeEnd=8040",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7951&rangeEnd=8040"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_4_3552-3615",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3552-3615",
      "markText": "中国历史上，像崇祯这样的皇帝不止一个，但是像崇祯这样能够不断地检讨自己，不断地反思，又不断地希望有所作为的皇帝，却并不是太多。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3552&rangeEnd=3615",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3552&rangeEnd=3615"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_12_467-542",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "467-542",
      "markText": "明朝由开放走向灭亡，而清朝由封闭走向强盛。这个说法指出了一种现象：晚明的社会是个开放社会，但是明朝最后亡了；清朝最强大的康乾盛世时期，却是相对封闭的。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_6_3475-3529",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3475-3529",
      "markText": "明朝的士大夫形成了很大的舆论势力，他们可以通过舆论鼓动群众，对内阁、皇帝进行压迫，但是他们从来不对后果负责。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3475&rangeEnd=3529",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3475&rangeEnd=3529"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_6_10847-10887",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10847-10887",
      "markText": "明朝的整个官场都被卷入党争之中。明朝的灭亡，无论是阉党还是东林党都应该承担责任。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10847&rangeEnd=10887",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10847&rangeEnd=10887"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_12_9493-9562",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "9493-9562",
      "markText": "明朝政府的最封闭之处是思维的封闭。官员唯恐出错，所以永远按照祖宗法度、圣贤道理来办事，这样可以不出错；一旦跳出三尺法，他们立即会被追究责任",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=9493&rangeEnd=9562",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=9493&rangeEnd=9562"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072452_8_2893-2964",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2893-2964",
      "markText": "历代明智的统治者都认为，地方官凶狠掠夺民众，实际上是在为朝廷招怨。因为民众不但会把怒气对准个别官员，更会把怒气对准朝廷，认为是朝廷没管好下属。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072452&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2893&rangeEnd=2964",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b6432e50813ab82cdg012246?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2893&rangeEnd=2964"
    },
    {
